    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Still photograph</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1943</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still photograph shows a man and woman sitting in front of two trees. They are holding each other’s hands. Four men are standing to their right, two men to their left. They are of various ages and wearing peasant costume, except the man on the left margin of the picture who is in uniform.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Dertli pinar’ (A dry summer) was directed by Faruk Kenҫ and was released in 1943.</ab>
